{
  "stem": "9665.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said Sally Noach was a very capable man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think he was a Dutchman, but he came from Entwerp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I might be wrong.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He might also have been from Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I introduced him to Jacquet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Sally Noach was a terrific help for Jacquet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He helped hundreds and probably thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I myself met [? vis-a-vis ?] a man called Diamond.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this man Diamond had a contact who was the police.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I made a mistake.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This has happened before I went to Marseille, I met Diamond, and-- because otherwise, we wouldn't have traveled.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He had a contact to the police and he filled in a piece of paper that we made an application to the police to stay in Lyon.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the police gave the stamp on it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that legalized you as being in Lyon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And if you get a sauf-conduit, wherever it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It speaks by itself that I introduced this Diamond-- and he had a partner, but I can't think of his name.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the price which we paid could have been 10,000 francs, which wasn't really so much.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was a wonderful man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I don't know if he survived that war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And that piece of paper from the Diamond, from Mr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Diamond, went through the whole of our family who came out afterwards from Holland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The first one to arrive from Holland was my brother-in-law, Max Wolf, or Wolf, and my sister Bertha and the two sons.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Again, the same story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They arrived at the demarcation line.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there was some money for the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I don't know if they went via [INAUDIBLE] or anywhere else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But we found out if you give money for the [NON-ENGLISH], which was for the pocket, you get to Lyon.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
